headline: Global Data Centre & Cloud Expo Canada Launches This Week, Defining the Future of Digital Transformation
summary: TORONTO, October 02, 2025--Global Data Centre & Cloud Expo Canada is taking place on October 7–8 at The International Centre, Toronto.

headline: The9's Singapore Investee NYB Announce Plan to Go Nasdaq via US$1.5 Billion Business Combination with SPAC RF Acquisition Corp II
